---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Contacto – Consultoría y Soporte Técnico SmartTrap">
  <main class="contact-editorial">
    <!-- SOLID BRAND HERO -->
    <section class="expert-hero-solid">
      <div class="container">
        <span class="pre-title">CANAL DE ATENCIÓN PROFESIONAL</span>
        <h1>Hablemos de su <br/>Próximo Salto Tecnológico</h1>
        <p>Expertos en agronomía digital a su disposición para transformar datos en rentabilidad real.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <div class="container main-content">
      <div class="editorial-grid">
        <!-- COLUMN LEFT: CONTACT INFO -->
        <aside class="info-sidebar">
          
          <div class="contact-method">
            <div class="method-icon">
              <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-8.63-3.07 19.5 19.5 0 0 1-6-6 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-3.07-8.67A2 2 0 0 1 4.11 2h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 1.72c.127.96.361 1.903.7 2.81a2 2 0 0 1-.45 2.11L8.09 9.91a16 16 0 0 0 6 6l1.27-1.27a2 2 0 0 1 2.11-.45c.907.339 1.85.573 2.81.7A2 2 0 0 1 22 16.92z"></path></svg>
            </div>
            <div class="method-details">
              <h3>Departamento Comercial</h3>
              <a href="tel:+34621262286" class="method-link">+34 621 26 22 86</a>
              <p>Atención directa de Lunes a Viernes.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="contact-method">
            <div class="method-icon">
              <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><rect x="2" y="4" width="20" height="16" rx="2"></rect><path d="m22 7-8.97 5.7a1.94 1.94 0 0 1-2.06 0L2 7"></path></svg>
            </div>
            <div class="method-details">
              <h3>Consultas Técnicas</h3>
              <a href="mailto:ceo@smartfenix.es" class="method-link">ceo@smartfenix.es</a>
              <p>Respuesta técnica en menos de 24h.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="contact-method">
            <div class="method-icon">
              <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><path d="M21 10c0 7-9 13-9 13s-9-6-9-13a9 9 0 0 1 18 0z"></path><circle cx="12" cy="10" r="3"></circle></svg>
            </div>
            <div class="method-details">
              <h3>Sede Central</h3>
              <address class="method-link"><a href="https://maps.app.goo.gl/E5FxGmKk8Cm5Zo149" target="_blank" style="color: inherit; text-decoration: none;">C. Donantes de sangre, nº 4, local 4, 14120 Fuente Palmera, Córdoba</a></address>
              <div class="map-container">
                <iframe 
                  src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3161.4646700543663!2d-5.1065185!3d37.7126131!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0xd6d3969a531f82f%3A0xe530d170fac8ca0!2sC.%20Donantes%20de%20Sangre%2C%204%2C%2014120%20Fuente%20Palmera%2C%20C%C3%B3rdoba!5e0!3m2!1ses!2ses!4v1711191420126!5m2!1ses!2ses" 
                  width="100%" 
                  height="200" 
                  style="border:0;" 
                  allowfullscreen="" 
                  loading="lazy" 
                  referrerpolicy="no-referrer-when-downgrade">
                </iframe>
              </div>
              <p>Centro de operaciones técnicas y logística.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="support-brief">
            <p>¿Necesita soporte técnico inmediato? Nuestro equipo está a su disposición para cualquier duda sobre el sistema.</p>
          </div>
        </aside>

        <!-- COLUMN RIGHT: AUDIT FORM -->
        <section class="form-wrapper">
          <div class="form-card">
            <div class="section-label">01. INICIAR AUDITORÍA</div>
            <h2>Solicitud de Información Técnica</h2>
            <p class="form-intro">Describa sus necesidades y un ingeniero asignado a su zona revisará su caso personalmente.</p>

            <form 
              action="https://formspree.io/f/ceo@smartfenix.es" 
              method="POST"
              class="editorial-form"
            >
              <div class="form-row">
                <div class="input-group">
                  <label for="name">Nombre y Apellidos</label>
                  <input type="text" id="name" name="name" placeholder="Su nombre completo" required />
                </div>
                <div class="input-group">
                  <label for="email">Email Corporativo</label>
                  <input type="email" id="email" name="email" placeholder="email@finca.com" required />
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="input-group">
                <label for="topic">Área de Interés Principal</label>
                <select id="topic" name="topic" required>
                  <option value="" disabled selected>Seleccione un área...</option>
                  <option value="siex">Cuaderno de Campo Digital (SIEX/REA)</option>
                  <option value="suelo">Sensores de Suelo y Raíz</option>
                  <option value="planta">Fisiología de Planta (Hoja y Fruto)</option>
                  <option value="clima">Monitorización Meteorológica</option>
                  <option value="kit-digital">Kit Digital / Subvenciones</option>
                  <option value="fieldbee">Autoguiado RTK y Maquinaria</option>
                  <option value="prescripcion">Prescripción Digital Variable</option>
                  <option value="estiercoles">Gestión de Estiércoles</option>
                  <option value="trazabilidad">Trazabilidad GPS DARP</option>
                  <option value="asesoramiento">Asesoramiento Estratégico</option>
                  <option value="cooperativas">Soluciones para Cooperativas</option>
                  <option value="soporte">Soporte Técnico / Incidencia</option>
                  <option value="otro">Consulta General / Otro</option>
                </select>
              </div>

              <div class="input-group">
                <label for="message">Mensaje / Contexto del Proyecto</label>
                <textarea id="message" name="message" rows="5" placeholder="¿En qué fase de digitalización se encuentra su explotación?"></textarea>
              </div>

              <div class="form-actions">
                <button type="submit" class="btn-submit">Enviar Solicitud de Información</button>
                <p class="disclaimer">Al enviar, confirma que ha leído y acepta nuestra Política de Privacidad.</p>
              </div>
            </form>
          </div>
        </section>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- FAQ MINI-SECTION -->
    <section class="faq-strip grey-bg">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="faq-grid-v3">
          <div class="faq-v3-item">
            <h4>¿Tienen delegaciones físicas?</h4>
            <p>Nuestra base está en Granada, pero operamos de forma digital y presencial en toda España y Portugal.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-v3-item">
            <h4>¿Atienden a pequeños agricultores?</h4>
            <p>Nuestras soluciones escalan desde fincas familiares hasta grandes cooperativas agroindustriales.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-v3-item">
            <h4>¿Cuál es el coste de la auditoría?</h4>
            <p>La primera toma de contacto y el análisis de viabilidad técnica son completamente gratuitos.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style is:global>
  .contact-editorial {
    background: #FFFFFF;
    color: var(--color-charcoal);
  }

  .contact-editorial .container {
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 24px;
  }

  /* BRAND HERO CROSS-PAGE */
  .expert-hero-solid {
    padding: 160px 0 120px;
    background: #0B1A14 !important;
    color: #FFFFFF !important;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .expert-hero-solid .pre-title {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.4em;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7) !important;
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .expert-hero-solid h1 {
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 4rem); /* Unified max size 4rem */
    font-weight: 800;
    line-height: 1.15;
    margin-bottom: 30px;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    color: #FFFFFF !important;
  }

  .expert-hero-solid p {
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.9) !important;
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  /* EDITORIAL GRID SYSTEM */
  .contact-editorial .main-content {
    margin-top: 0;
    padding-top: 80px;
    padding-bottom: 120px;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 20;
  }

  .editorial-grid {
    display: grid !important;
    grid-template-columns: 360px 1fr !important;
    gap: 100px !important;
    align-items: start;
  }

  /* SIDEBAR INFO */
  .info-sidebar {
    padding-top: 0;
  }

  .contact-editorial .section-label {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.25em;
    color: var(--color-slate-700);
    opacity: 0.6;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
    display: block;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .contact-method {
    display: flex;
    gap: 24px;
    margin-bottom: 48px;
  }

  .method-icon {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 24px;
    height: 24px;
    color: var(--color-turquoise);
    margin-top: 4px;
  }

  .method-details h3 {
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    color: var(--color-slate-900);
  }

  .method-link {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-charcoal);
    text-decoration: none;
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .method-details p {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--color-gray-500);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .support-brief {
    margin-top: 60px;
    padding: 32px;
    background: var(--color-gray-50);
    border-radius: 20px;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-gray-100);
  }

  .support-brief p {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    color: var(--color-slate-700);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .text-link {
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-turquoise);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    transition: opacity 0.3s ease;
  }

  .text-link:hover {
    opacity: 0.8;
  }

  .map-container {
    margin: 20px 0;
    border-radius: 20px;
    overflow: hidden;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-gray-100);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
    filter: grayscale(0.2);
    transition: filter 0.3s ease;
  }

  .map-container:hover {
    filter: grayscale(0);
  }

  /* FORM CARD DESIGN */
  .form-card {
    background: #FFFFFF !important;
    padding: 70px !important;
    border-radius: 32px !important;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-gray-100) !important;
    box-shadow: 0 40px 100px -20px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.08) !important;
  }

  .form-card h2 {
    font-size: 2.6rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    color: var(--color-slate-900) !important;
  }

  .form-intro {
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    color: var(--color-slate-700);
    margin-bottom: 50px;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  /* EDITORIAL FORM FIELDS */
  .editorial-form {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 32px;
  }

  .form-row {
    display: grid !important;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr !important;
    gap: 32px !important;
  }

  .input-group {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 12px;
  }

  .input-group label {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: var(--color-slate-800) !important;
  }

  .input-group input,
  .input-group select,
  .input-group textarea {
    padding: 18px 22px !important;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-gray-200) !important;
    border-radius: 14px !important;
    background: var(--color-white) !important;
    font-size: 1.05rem !important;
    font-family: inherit;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    color: var(--color-slate-900) !important;
  }

  .input-group input::placeholder,
  .input-group textarea::placeholder {
    color: var(--color-gray-500) !important;
    opacity: 0.6;
  }

  .input-group input:focus,
  .input-group select:focus,
  .input-group textarea:focus {
    outline: none;
    border-color: var(--color-turquoise) !important;
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px rgba(15, 181, 174, 0.1) !important;
  }

  .btn-submit {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    padding: 22px;
    background: var(--color-turquoise) !important;
    color: #FFFFFF !important;
    border: none;
    border-radius: 14px;
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.165, 0.84, 0.44, 1);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 25px -5px rgba(15, 181, 174, 0.3);
  }

  .btn-submit:hover {
    transform: translateY(-3px);
    box-shadow: 0 20px 40px -10px rgba(15, 181, 174, 0.4);
    background: var(--color-turquoise-dark) !important;
  }

  .disclaimer {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--color-gray-500);
    text-align: center;
    margin-top: 24px;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  /* FAQ STRIP */
  .faq-strip {
    padding: 100px 0;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-gray-100);
    background: var(--color-gray-50);
  }

  .faq-grid-v3 {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 60px;
  }

  .faq-v3-item h4 {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    color: var(--color-slate-900);
  }

  .faq-v3-item p {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--color-slate-700);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  @media (max-width: 1100px) {
    .editorial-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr !important;
      gap: 80px;
    }
    .info-sidebar { order: 2; }
    .form-wrapper { order: 1; }
    .form-card { padding: 40px !important; }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .form-row { grid-template-columns: 1fr !important; gap: 24px !important; }
    .expert-hero-solid h1 { font-size: 2.4rem !important; }
    .form-card h2 { font-size: 2rem !important; }
  }
</style>
